"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 19, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever practices medicine without any prior knowledge of medicine will be held liable.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3466 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0645\u0652\u0631\u0650\u0648 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42054,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/07\/24\/ibn-masud-ask-scholars\/","url_meta":{"origin":32641,"position":2},"title":"Ibn Mas\u2019ud on Doubt: Ask the scholars, if you can find them","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 24, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Wa\u2019il reported: Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud, may Allah be pleased with him, said, \u201cVerily, one of you will remain good as long as he fears Allah. If you find doubt within yourself about something, ask a man to cure you from it, but soon you will not be able to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32697,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/06\/scholars-with-ignorant-hearts\/","url_meta":{"origin":32641,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Hypocrisy: The Prophet fears scholars with ignorant hearts","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 6, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Umar ibn al-Khattab reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among what I fear most for my nation is every hypocrite with a knowledgeable tongue.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323mad 140 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Ahmad Shakir \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u062e\u064e\u0637\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651 \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":31955,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/11\/learning-youth-sign-hour\/","url_meta":{"origin":32641,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ignorance: Learning from young a sign of the Hour","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 11, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Umayyah reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, among the signs of the Hour is that knowledge will be sought from the youth.\u201d Source: al-Mu\u2019jam al-Kabi\u0304r lil-T\u0323abara\u0304ni\u0304 22\/361 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0623\u064f\u0645\u064e\u064a\u0651\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u062e\u0652\u0645\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u064e \u